flowRoot.flowPara: As we all know, little doors are portals to magical places. They can lead one to gnomes, fairies, and may other types of magical creatures! Come join us in creating your own mini magical door to share with your friends
Once complete, you may choose to install your door in one of our special places within Mt. Pleasant. Secret codes will lead you from one door to the next until you find them all!
The top secret map can be downloaded at

text.tspan: FREE! Space is limited to 25 people.
Kids of all ages welcome - from 1 t 110!

flowRoot.flowPara: All required materials will be provided, however you are encouraged to bring any magical, shiny, spacey, or crafty additions to make your magical door even more special
